Jimin is apart of a special team of people whose job is to ward off Shadows from those around the world at night. The only problem is, all the years he’s spent warding evil away from Jeongguk has reverted onto Jimin and corrupted him. And now he’s turned against the angel he’s spent his life protecting.

by bucephalas

“Hello,” said Seokjin. If there was one thing he was good at, it was keeping his cool in front of hot guys. Confidence did that for you. “Did you know you’re stealing all my customers?”

Seokjin never expected to meet famous rapper Kim Namjoon at one of his lectures on Wong Kar Wai. But life was rarely what you expected.
